author: markt
msg: Add support for running Tomcat 6 with ecj-P20140317-1600.jar (as drop-in replacement for ecj-4.3.1.jar).
Add support for value "1.8" for the compilerSourceVM and compilerTargetVM options.
Note that ecj-P20140317-1600.jar can only be used when running with Java 6 or later. The "1.8" options make sense only when running with Java 8 (or later).
